{
  "id": "adv_card_smr_13_01",
  "title": "奥山すみれ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――星見プロ全国ツアー大阪公演前日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "さっき食べたたこ焼き、美味しかったね！\n東京で食べるたこ焼きとは、どこか違った気がする",
      "startTime": 6.6333335399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.4333335399
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "関東のたこ焼きは、表面をカリッと揚げ焼きにしている\nお店が多いそうですね。関西は逆に、フワッと焼くとか",
      "startTime": 15.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 20.2799094041
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "へ～、名前は同じなのに焼き方が違うんだ\nお好み焼きも違ったりするのかな？",
      "startTime": 25.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "さっき通ったお店で売ってたよね\nせっかくだし、食べに行こうかな！",
      "startTime": 31.4000003815,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.1799090227
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "いいですね～。こういう食べ歩きこそ遠征の\n醍醐味と言っても過言じゃないですよ",
      "startTime": 38.1333337148,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.9365076226
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよね！　{user}さん\nこの後のことについてなんですけど",
      "startTime": 44.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 46.7698422274
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、すまない。伝えていなかったな\nそろそろホテルのチェックイン時間なんだ",
      "startTime": 49.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "移動の疲れもあるだろう\n明日も早いし、休める時にはゆっくり休んでおいてくれ",
      "startTime": 54.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.003176578
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "えっ……あ、そうですよね\n明日も早いですし……あはは……",
      "startTime": 62.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 66.3365063509
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "えー。まだお昼なのに、もうホテルに行くんですか？\nすみれちゃんだって、本当はもっと遊びたいですよね？",
      "startTime": 70.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 74.6081415337
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "で、でも、明日からライブだから\n休まなきゃいけないのはその通りだと思うよ",
      "startTime": 77.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.3414784274
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅん？　まぁ一理ありますし、仕方ないですね\n先生の言うことはちゃんと聞かないといけませんし？",
      "startTime": 87.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.3000025432
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "先生じゃなくてマネージャーなんだが……\nほら、ホテルに行くぞ。はぐれないようにな",
      "startTime": 94.3000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.9190097335
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "はーい。可愛いこころをホテルまでちゃんと\nエスコートして下さいね～",
      "startTime": 101.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_osaka-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "osaka-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.9045655095
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと食べてみたかったけど、ダメだよね……\nライブのためにも休まなくっちゃ……",
      "startTime": 108.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ホテル到着後",
      "startTime": 112.0666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4766.666666600003,
          "startTime": 116.8333333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.3333307902
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 113.3333307902
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "行きたかったお店、美味しいって評判だったんだ……\n本場のお好み焼き、食べてみたかったなぁ",
      "startTime": 119.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "ううん、大阪にはお仕事のために来てるんだから\nいつまでも観光気分でいちゃダメだよね",
      "startTime": 129.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.9045466903
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "本当にそれでいいんですか？\n大阪、もっと楽しみたくないですか～？",
      "startTime": 134.63331604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 137.9737602078
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "わっ！？　び、びっくりした\nいきなり顔を覗き込まないでよ",
      "startTime": 140.5666564941,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.5404360298
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "すみれちゃんこそ、話しかけても上の空だった\nじゃないですかー。せっかく同じ部屋になれたのに",
      "startTime": 146.8333231608,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.7510408246
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "でも、やっぱりすみれちゃんも、もっと遊びたかったん\nですね～。お好み焼きに想いを馳せるぐらいですし",
      "startTime": 155.0999898274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 159.4512629673
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-smr011.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それは……私だって遊びたい、けど……\n{user}さんは早めに休めって……",
      "startTime": 165.4666564941,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 168.9179296339
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "我慢は体に毒だと思うんですよね～\nほら、ストレスは肌荒れの原因とも言いますし",
      "startTime": 172.5999898274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 176.5978165791
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-smr012.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだっちゃ……！　こないだ優ちゃんも\nストレスはお肌に良くないって……で、でもなぁ……",
      "startTime": 180.7666564941,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 186.7644832457
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "もやもやしたままじゃ、ライブにも身が入らないかも？\nそれに、お口はもうお好み焼きの口になってますよねぇ",
      "startTime": 191.4999898274,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_okinawahotel-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "okinawahotel-00-noon",
      "startTime": 197.1255940602
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01/sud_vo_adv_card_smr_13_01-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "ほら、熱々でふわっふわなお好み焼きがすみれちゃんを\n待ってますよ？　ジューシーな豚まんもありましたよ～",
      "startTime": 203.5999898274,
      "sfxList": []
